      "text": "Problem:\ncreate_session()\nonly deletes expired\nsessions, not the\nuser's current active\nsession\nImpact: Users can\nhave multiple valid\nsessions\nsimultaneously",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "8TlMo6EAaooYcocKiZoNp",
      "originalText": "Problem: create_session() only deletes expired sessions, not the user's current active session\nImpact: Users can have multiple valid sessions simultaneously",
